<title>HONG KONG: Universal 1996 net loss HK$69.22 mln.</title>
<headline>Universal 1996 net loss HK$69.22 mln.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended December 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   7.62 loss  vs 3.98 loss</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    nil	  vs nil</p>
